<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,user-scalable=0,minimum-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
    <title>福利发放</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/component.min.css">
</head>
<body class="ovfHiden qiao">

<div class="panel-body panel-body-shodow">
    <h2>福利发放
        <div>
            <a href="../Welfare_release_record/new_release_details.html" class="show_details">查看发放明细</a>
        </div>
    </h2>

    <!--导航-->
    <div class="welfare_nav">
        <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
            <li><a href="part_release.html">部分发放</a></li>
            <li><a href="all_release.html">全体员工</a></li>
            <li class="active"><a href="#">批量发放</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!--组件-->

    <div class="smodal_content">
        <div class="info_content modal22">
            <span>发放账户：</span>
                <span>
                    <span class="radio_boxs">
                         <label>
                             <input type="radio" name="account" checked>福利账户
                         </label>
                    </span>

                    <span class="radio_boxs">
                        <label>
                            <input type="radio" name="account">现金账户
                        </label>
                    </span>
                </span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="smodal_content">
        <div class=" info_content modal22">
            <span class="release_account">福利账户余额：</span>
            <span >10,000.00</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="smodal_content">
        <div class="info_content modal22">
            <span><span class="add_star">*</span>选择文件：</span>
        <span>

            <div class="right_text">
                <a href="#" class="choose_file">
                    <input type="file">
                    <span>选择</span>
                </a>
                <span class="file_resourse">未选择文件</span>
                <p>限Excel文件，不能超过2M</p>
            </div>
        </span>
        </div>
    </div>



    <%- include('../../component/button/oneButton.ejs',{
    "thisurl":"release_comfirm.html",
    "buttontext":"下一步"

    })%>

<!--导入说明-->
    <div class="batch_import_info">

        <div class="import_content" style="display: block">
            <div class="content_top" style="margin-top: 30px">
                <h4 class="text-left import_info">导入说明</h4>
                <p class="text-left"><span>1、导入文件格式为Excel格式，后缀名为.xls或.xlsx</span><button  class="welfare_release_downbtn">下载附件</button></p>
                <p class="text-left">2、导入的数据应该放在文件的第一个工作表中，并按模板提示填写，工作表结构如下：</p>
                <div class="table-responsive info_table show_table">
                    <table class="table table-bordered">
                        <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th><span class="add_redstar">*</span>员工邮箱</th>
                            <th><span class="add_redstar">*</span>员工姓名</th>
                            <th><span class="add_redstar">*</span>发放金额（元）</th>
                            <th>备注（20字以内）</th>
                        </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>19625865056@qq.com</td>
                            <td>小王</td>
                            <td>100.00</td>
                            <td>夏日高温费</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>19625865056@qq.com</td>
                            <td>小王</td>
                            <td>100.00</td>
                            <td>夏日高温费</td>
                        </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="content_mid">
                <p class="text-left">3、员工姓名、邮箱、发放金额为必填</p>
                <p class="text-left">4、每次最多可导入500条福利信息</p>
                <p class="text-left">5、发放总金额超过xxx元（含），嘉福平台返利1%至员工账户（配置后显示）</p>
            </div>
        </div>



    </div>


</div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-3.0.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/BusinessService.min.js"></script>
<script>

    //点击切换发放账户
    $('label').on("click",function(){

        if($(this).find('input[type=radio]').is(":checked")){//当前是否选中

            var thisInnerText=$(this).text().replace(/(^\s*)|(\s*$)/g, "");//去除空格

            thisInnerText=thisInnerText+'余额：';

            $('.release_account').text(thisInnerText)

        }

    })
</script>
</body>
</html>